info.author: Reimar Bauer
info.description:
moin_plugin_mathjax
-------------------

This package is experimental!

It is used to install the xstatic-mathjax package
and configures it for moin-2.0

mathjax is a formular editor, a simple example:

{{{

$
\alpha
\beta
$

}}}


For further examples see http://www.mathjax.org
